Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小點心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小點心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有一些簡單貨色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次做的芝士蛋糕應該剩下些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:58.81,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某T：這裡指的是免烤日式芝士蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先讓奶油在常溫下解凍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子 這個拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在融化在融化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是廚具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕下麵用碎餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和少量牛奶混合做成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這個要做底部的 別吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:28.00,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某T：雞蛋 白砂糖 麵粉做的蛋糕墊底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
